sentences.sentence: As I inhale the impalpable breezes that set in upon me.

sentences.sentence: Purpose: To review the use of laparoscopy in the management of impalpable testes in children.

sentences.sentence: But words are more impalpable than bricks reading is a longer and more complicated process than seeing.
